Problem resides in `src/models/article_filters.rs`

The `unread` filter doesn't actually filter unread articles, but doesn't filter anything at all.

Changing the function as follows solves the problem:

```
    pub fn unread() -> Self {
        let mut filter = ArticlesFilter::default();
        filter.archived = Some(false);
        filter
    }
```

I think I don't have enough rights on the repository to create a MR and a branch from this issue, so I will create it on my forked repo and push a MR to this repo at a moment today.

